      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color:rgba(106,132,166,.88)">Open to all participants aged 21 and older \'97 including university students, graduate researchers, independent scholars, and lifelong learners. Work in this division is held to the highest standard of academic rigor.</p>\
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">\
