        <div><div class="eyebrow mb-1" style="font-size:.57rem">Digital Experience</div><h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-cream">Visio Interactivus</h3></div>\
      </div>\
      <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed mb-4" style="color:rgba(106,132,166,.9)">Websites, apps, or data visualizations where users explore a historical question nonlinearly. The historical argument must be embedded in the design of the experience itself.</p>\
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center"><span class="text-xs" style="color:rgba(212,175,55,.52)">Teams 1\'964 \'b7 Adulescens &amp; Adultus</span><span class="text-xs flex items-center gap-1" style="color:var(--gold)">Details <svg width="11" height="11" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></span></div>\
